      <example>
         <p>The %rel-atts; parameter entity is used within the DITA dtds
as a common definition for attributes available to elements that represent
topic-to-topic relationships. Not all of these capabilities have been provided
yet for DITA topic processing. Some typical examples include:</p>
         <pre>&lt;link type="task" role="child" href="how2uninst.xml" scope="local"/&gt;</pre>
      </example>
